set adjust-open width


map j scroll half-down
map k scroll half-up
map J zoom out
map K zoom in
map - zoom out
map = zoom in
map _ adjust_window best-fit
map + adjust_window width

map r reload
map R rotate

map <C-n> search forward
map <C-b> search backward

#access index w tab
#colon tab for options
#colon number to land on page no or nG
#map p print

map f toggle_fullscreen
